query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mi.info in ('Tlingit','Korean','Danish','Ukrainian','Slovenian','Czech','Latin','Dari','Macedonian','Ladino','Spanish','Bosnian') AND (k.keyword like '%music%' OR k.keyword like '%warrior%' OR k.keyword like '%warfare%') AND it1.info in ('salary history','LD video artifacts','locations','spouse','LD dialogue intellegibility','LD release date','LD audio quality','LD label','essays','LD color information','LD spaciality','LD contrast','screenplay-teleplay','countries') AND (n.name like '%e%') AND n.gender not in ('f') AND cct2.kind not in ('complete','crew') AND it2.info in ('votes','salary history') AND cct1.kind in ('complete','complete+verified','cast') AND (t.title like '%dream%' OR t.title like '%key%' OR t.title like '%shield%' OR t.title like '%dress%' OR t.title like '%love%') AND mi_idx.info < '6.0'
